<%
// Crane Tree Removal Service Page
%>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="page-header" style="background-image: url('/images/port-orford.jpg');">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Crane Tree Removal in Gold Beach, OR</h1>
        <p>Professional Crane Assisted Tree Service on the Oregon Coast</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="service-detail section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- Introduction with Image -->
        <div class="service-intro">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <p>JT & Sons Tree Service LLC provides safe and professional crane tree removal in Gold Beach, OR and surrounding areas including Brookings, Pistol River, Ophir, Agnes, Port Orford, Sixes, Langlois, Bandon, and Coos Bay.</p>
                <p>Some tree removals require specialized equipment due to tree size, location, or nearby structures. Our crane assisted tree services allow us to safely remove large or hazardous trees while protecting your home, property, and landscape.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="intro-image">
                <img src="/images/crane1.jpg" alt="Crane Tree Removal" class="rounded-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- When Crane Services Are Needed -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>When Crane Tree Services Are Needed</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Large Tree Removal</strong> – Very large or mature trees often require cranes to safely lift and remove heavy sections.</li>
                <li><strong>Trees Near Homes or Structures</strong> – When trees grow close to buildings, fences, or power lines, crane-assisted removal allows precise and controlled removal.</li>
                <li><strong>Difficult Access Tree Removal</strong> – Trees located in tight spaces or hard-to-reach areas can be safely removed using crane equipment.</li>
                <li><strong>Storm-Damaged Trees</strong> – After storms, broken or unstable trees may require crane services for safe removal.</li>
                <li><strong>Emergency Tree Removal</strong> – In emergency situations where a tree has fallen or is dangerously leaning, cranes can help remove the tree quickly.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefits + Image Row -->
        <div class="service-include-row">
            <div class="service-list">
                <h2>Benefits of Crane Assisted Tree Removal</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Improved Safety</strong> – Crane-assisted removal reduces the risk of accidents by allowing controlled lifting of heavy sections.</li>
                    <li><strong>Faster Tree Removal</strong> – Using a crane allows our crew to remove large trees more efficiently.</li>
                    <li><strong>Better Property Protection</strong> – Crane tree removal minimizes impact on your yard, landscaping, and nearby structures.</li>
                    <li><strong>Access to Hard-to-Reach Trees</strong> – Crane equipment allows our team to safely work on trees in challenging locations.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="service-image">
                <img src="/images/crane2.jpg" alt="Crane in Action" class="rounded-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Process -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>Our Crane Tree Service Process</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Tree Evaluation</strong> – Our team evaluates the size, condition, and location of the tree to determine the safest crane removal method.</li>
                <li><strong>Crane Setup & Safety Planning</strong> – We carefully position the crane and establish safety measures for a smooth removal process.</li>
                <li><strong>Crane Assisted Tree Removal</strong> – Large tree sections are carefully lifted and removed using the crane, preventing damage to surrounding property.</li>
                <li><strong>Cleanup & Property Restoration</strong> – After the removal, we clean up all debris and ensure your property is left safe and tidy.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Info Box -->
        <div class="contact-info-box">
            <h3>Get a Free Crane Tree Removal Estimate</h3>
            <p>
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Office: <a href="tel:<%= sitePhone %>"><%= sitePhone %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Cell/Text: <a href="tel:<%= siteCell %>"><%= siteCell %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: <a href="mailto:<%= siteEmail %>"><%= siteEmail %></a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>